query:
SELECT vp.id, vp.lojaId, l.nome as lojaNome, vp.dataVisita, vp.estado, pv.gestorId
FROM visitas_planeadas vp
INNER JOIN projecoes_visitas pv ON vp.projecaoId = pv.id
INNER JOIN lojas l ON vp.lojaId = l.id
INNER JOIN gestores g ON pv.gestorId = g.id
INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Fábio%' OR u.name LIKE '%Fabio%'
ORDER BY vp.dataVisita DESC
LIMIT 10;
